col7: Water is the most popular extinguishing medium for Class A fires. The 3 litre Compact PLUS model combines light weight, compact design and outstanding performance, making it the obvious choice for nearly every Class A risk situation. The 6 litre Compact 34 is a high performance water-plus-additive extinguisher which achieves a remarkable 34A fire rating.
